@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mjekht(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    tmp = wp.abs((v1 / wp.abs(v2 + 0.33)))
    v2 = 0.09
    tmp = (wp.exp(tmp) + ((tmp + 0.73 - v1 + 0.55) * (tmp + 0.11 * v0 + 0.24)))
    tmp = wp.cos((v0 - v2))
    v2 = (0.62 * wp.cos(v0))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.54 * v2 + 0.21)) * ((v1 + 0.38 - v1 + 0.50) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.95)))
    data[tid] = v0
